window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Haunting, harrowing, and downright horrifying, this classic collection from the modern master of the fantastic features: </p> <ul> <li>\"The Small Assassin\": a fine, healthy baby boy was the new mother's dream come true - or her nightmare.... </li> <li>\"The Emissary\": the faithful dog was the sick boy's only connection with the world outside - and beyond.... </li> <li>\"The Wonderful Death of Dudley Stone\": a most remarkable case of murder - the deceased was delighted! </li> <li>And more!</li> </ul>"; 
